#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.isna.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.isna"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna:1 of
msgid "Detect missing values."
msgstr "检测缺失值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna:3 of
msgid ""
"Return a boolean same-sized object indicating if the values are NA. NA "
"values, such as None or :attr:`numpy.NaN`, gets mapped to True values."
msgstr ""
"返回一个与原对象大小相同的布尔对象，用于指示值是否为 NA。NA 值，例如 None"
" 或 :attr:`numpy.NaN`，将被映射为 True。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna:7 of
msgid ""
"Everything else gets mapped to False values. Characters such as empty "
"strings ``''`` or :attr:`numpy.inf` are not considered NA values (unless "
"you set ``pandas.options.mode.use_inf_as_na = True``)."
msgstr ""
"其他所有内容都会被映射为 False。空字符串 ``''`` 或 :attr:`numpy.inf` 等"
"字符不被视为 NA 值（除非你设置了 ``pandas.options.mode.use_inf_as_na = "
"True``）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna:11 of
msgid ""
"Mask of bool values for each element in DataFrame that indicates whether "
"an element is not an NA value."
msgstr "一个与 DataFrame 中每个元素对应的布尔值掩码，用于指示元素是否不是 NA 值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna:17 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.isnull`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna:18 of
msgid "Alias of isna."
msgstr "isna 的别名。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna:20 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.notna`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna:21 of
msgid "Boolean inverse of isna."
msgstr "isna 的布尔反值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna:23 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.dropna`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna:24 of
msgid "Omit axes labels with missing values."
msgstr "删除包含缺失值的轴标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`isna`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna:27 of
msgid "Top-level isna."
msgstr "顶层 isna 函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna:30 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna:31 of
msgid "Show which entries in a DataFrame are NA."
msgstr "显示 DataFrame 中哪些条目是 NA。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.isna:52 of
msgid "Show which entries in a Series are NA."
msgstr "显示 Series 中哪些条目是 NA。"

